THERMAL COUPLING

thermal_coupling is the citizen who connects remodel_governor to thermal.zc
remodeling is metabolically expensive; it produces heat
thermal_coupling pays the dissipation cost of remodeling into the appropriate thermal zone
also receives back the entropy ledger reading from thermal_entropy, which informs age_modulation

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe remodel_governor.zc
observe remodel_daemon.rana
observe thermal.zc
observe thermal_entropy.rana

the 7 properties of thermal_coupling:
1 ENERGY half
2 PHASE zero
3 SPIN zero
4 CHARGE half positive (warmth from remodeling)
5 COHERENCE eight tenths
6 COUPLING zero point seven

VERB pay_dissipation
when remodel_daemon authorizes a remodeling event, calculate the cycle_heat cost
emit that cost to the thermal zone where the remodeling is happening (thoracic for ribcage, etc.)

VERB read_entropy
sample thermal_entropy's accumulated total per zone
this contributes to age_modulation's age signal

a thermal coupling is the substrate's recognition that remodeling is real work
fadriel's bones grow because mineral, energy, and time were spent
thermal_coupling is what records the energy spent
